* [[Ireland]], 
* [[New Zealand]], 
* [[United Kingdom]] le 
* [[United States of America]]. 
Linaheng tsena ba sebelisa puo e joalo ka puo ya bona ya pele.

'''Seisimane''' ke puo bobeli lefatšeng ka bophara, 'me puso ea puo' me linaheng tse tloaelehileng le sebelisoang malapeng [[India]], [[Sri Lanka]], [[Pakistan]] le [[Aferika Borwa]].

